  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <p xml:id="NA64-kiḷavi">itu piriviṭait talaiviya tarumai kaṇṭu tūtuviṭak karutiya tōḻikkut talaivi colliyatu.</p>
        <p xml:lang="en">This is what SHE said to the confidante who intended to send a messenger fter seeing HER difficulties in the time of separation.</p>
      </div>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <lg xml:id="NA64">
<l>            eṉṉa rāyiṉu miṉiniṉai voḻika</l>
<l>            vaṉṉa vāka viṉaiyaṟ ṟōḻi</l>
<l>            yiṉṉa mākat tuṟantōr naṭpeṉa</l>
<l>            maraṉā ruṭukkai malaiyuṟai kuṟava</l>
<l>            raṟiyā taṟutta ciṟiyilaic cāntam </l>
<l>            vaṟaṉuṟ ṟāra murukkip paiyeṉa</l>
<l>            maramvaṟi tākac cōrntuk kāṅke</l>
<l>            ṉaṟivu muḷḷamu mavarvayiṟ ceṉṟeṉa</l>
<l>            vaṟitā likuḷaiyeṉ yākkai yiṉiyavar</l>
<l>            variṉu nōymarun tallar vārā </l>
<l>            tavaṇa rākuka kātala rivaṇaṅ</l>
<l>            kāmam paṭaraṭa varuntiya</l>
<l>            nōymali varuttaṅ kāṇaṉmā remarē.</l>
            </lg>
       <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Of whatever kind he may be, let the thought stay behind now.</l>
<l>Since things are thus, don't despair, friend.</l>
<l rend="indent4">[Thinking]</l>
<l rend="indent">“he is one that has abandoned [our] intimacy, for us to become thus”,</l>
<l>my body is empty in fact,</l>
<l rend="indent2">because knowledge and mind have gone to him,</l>
<l rend="indent2">as a sandal tree with small leaves, that have been cut off</l>
<l rend="indent3">unknowingly by the mountain-dwelling hill people,</l>
<l rend="indent3">with [their] garments of hemp fibre,</l>
<l rend="indent2">is fully ruined by draught, languishes [and] sheds [its foliage],</l>
<l rend="indent4">so that the tree slowly becomes empty.</l>
<l rend="indent4">Now, even if</l>
<l>he comes, he is not a remedy for the ill.</l>
<l>Let him be in that place without coming [back], [our] lover.</l>
<l>Let our [man] not see the suffering increased by pain</l>
<l rend="indent4">
    <choice>
    <seg>suffered so that affliction killed our desire, here.</seg>
    <seg>suffered so that the affliction of desire kills us here.</seg>
</choice></l>
        </lg>
         </div>
          </body>
